e Resolution","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties shall first attempt to resolve any dispute arising out of this Agreement through good-faith negotiation. If the dispute is not resolved within thirty (30) days, the parties agree to submit the dispute to binding arbitration or, where the parties mutually agree, mediation, prior to pursuing court litigation, except where injunctive relief is required."},{"name":"assignment_clause","label":"Assignment","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Neither party may assign or transfer its rights or obligations under this Agreement without the prior written consent of the other party, except in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of substantially all of its assets."},{"name":"entire_agreement_clause","label":"Entire Agreement","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to its subject matter and supersedes all prior or contemporaneous agreements, understandings, and communications, whether written or oral."},{"name":"severability_clause","label":"Severability","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"If any provision of this Agreement is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect, and the invalid provision shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it enforceable."},{"name":"electronic_signature_clause","label":"Electronic Signature","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"The parties agree that this Agreement may be executed electronically and that electronic signatures, including typed, drawn, or uploaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"non_solicitation_clause","label":"Non-Solicitation","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"During the term of this Agreement and for twelve (12) months thereafter, neither party shall solicit for hire any employee or contractor of the other party, nor solicit the other party''s clients or customers for competing purposes, without prior written consent."},{"name":"non_compete_clause","label":"Non-Compete","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Where legally permitted, each party agrees not to engage in any business directly competing with the other party''s business within the same market for a reasonable period following termination of this Agreement, to the extent enforceable under applicable law."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"founder_one_signature","label":"Founder One Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"founder_two_signature","label":"Founder Two Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}' WHERE slug = 'founders-agreement-generator';
