loaded signatures, shall have the same legal effect as handwritten signatures."},{"name":"data_protection_clause","label":"Data Protection & Privacy","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Each party shall handle any personal data obtained in connection with this Agreement in accordance with applicable data protection laws (including, where applicable, GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, or PIPEDA) and shall implement reasonable safeguards against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of such data."},{"name":"non_solicitation_clause","label":"Non-Solicitation","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"During the term of this Agreement and for twelve (12) months thereafter, neither party shall solicit for hire any employee or contractor of the other party, nor solicit the other party''s clients or customers for competing purposes, without prior written consent."},{"name":"change_request_clause","label":"Change Requests","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Any changes to the scope described in this Agreement must be agreed in writing by both parties, including any associated adjustments to fees or timelines, before such changes take effect."},{"name":"insurance_clause","label":"Insurance","type":"textarea","required":false,"default":"Where applicable, each party shall maintain insurance coverage appropriate to its obligations under this Agreement and shall provide proof of such coverage upon the other party''s reasonable request."},{"name":"governing_law","label":"Governing Law / Jurisdiction","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"additional_terms","label":"Additional Terms & Conditions","type":"textarea","required":false},{"name":"witness_name","label":"Witness Name (optional)","type":"text","required":false},{"name":"licensor_signature","label":"Licensor Signature","type":"signature","required":false},{"name":"licensee_signature","label":"Licensee Signature","type":"signature","required":false}]}', '[{"q":"Is the Licensing Agreement Generator free to use?